User-Defined Operators (C++/CLI)](../../dotnet/user-defined-operators-cpp-cli.md).  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C2581.  \n  \n```  \n// C2581.cpp  \n// compile with: /clr /c  \nref struct Y {  \n   static Y ^ operator = (Y^ me, int i);   // C2581  \n   Y^ operator =(int i);   // OK  \n};  \n```"}